#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:9
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>Man</title>"
msgstr "<title>नरः</title>"

#. Tag: author
#: index.docbook:12
#, no-c-format
msgid "&Lauri.Watts; &Lauri.Watts.mail;"
msgstr "&लौरी.वाट्स; &लौरी.वाट्स.मेल;"

#. Tag: author
#: index.docbook:13
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<firstname>Nicolas</firstname> <surname>Goutte</surname> <email>goutte@kde."
"org</email>"
msgstr ""
"<प्रथमनाम>निकोलस</firstname> <उपनाम>गौट्</surname> <email>goutte@kde.org</"
"email>"

#. Tag: trans_comment
#: index.docbook:18
#, no-c-format
msgid "ROLES_OF_TRANSLATORS"
msgstr "अनुवादकानां_भूमिका"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:22
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Using the man KIO worker you are able to read the man pages installed on "
"your system. It is easy to use:"
msgstr ""
"man KIO worker इत्यस्य उपयोगेन भवान् स्वस्य प्रणाल्यां संस्थापितानि man पृष्ठानि पठितुं "
"समर्थः भवति । अस्य उपयोगः सुलभः अस्ति :"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:31
#, no-c-format
msgid "See the sections of the manual, click to find the rest."
msgstr "पुस्तिकायाः विभागान् पश्यन्तु, शेषं अन्वेष्टुं क्लिक् कुर्वन्तु ।"

#. Tag: userinput
#: index.docbook:36
#, no-c-format
msgid "<command>man:/</command><replaceable>fopen</replaceable>"
msgstr "<command>man:/</command><replaceable>fopen</replaceable> इति"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:38
#, no-c-format
msgid "See the man page of <command>fopen</command>."
msgstr "<command>fopen</command> इत्यस्य man पृष्ठं पश्यन्तु ।"

#. Tag: userinput
#: index.docbook:43
#, no-c-format
msgid "<command>man:/</command><replaceable>fopen(3)</replaceable>"
msgstr "<command>man:/</command><replaceable>fopen(3)</replaceable> इति"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:45
#, no-c-format
msgid "See the man page of <command>fopen</command> in section 3."
msgstr "खण्डे ३ <command>fopen</command> इत्यस्य man पृष्ठं पश्यन्तु ।"

#. Tag: userinput
#: index.docbook:50
#, no-c-format
msgid "<command>man:/</command><replaceable>(3)</replaceable>"
msgstr "<command>man:/</command><replaceable>(3)</replaceable> इति"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:52
#, no-c-format
msgid "See the index of section 3."
msgstr "खण्डस्य ३ अनुक्रमणिकां पश्यन्तु ।"

#. Tag: userinput
#: index.docbook:57
#, no-c-format
msgid "<command>man:/</command>intro<replaceable>(3)</replaceable>"
msgstr "<command>man:/</command>intro<प्रतिस्थापनीय>(3)</प्रतिस्थापनीय>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:59
#, no-c-format
msgid "See the introduction of section 3."
msgstr "खण्डस्य ३ परिचयं पश्यन्तु ।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:65
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If there are more than one man page of the name that you have entered, you "
"will get a list where you can choose the man page that you want to see."
msgstr ""
"यदि भवता प्रविष्टस्य नामस्य एकादशाधिकं man पृष्ठं भवति तर्हि भवान् एकां सूचीं प्राप्स्यति "
"यत्र भवान् यत् man पृष्ठं द्रष्टुम् इच्छति तत् चिन्वितुं शक्नोति ।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:69
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"There is also a shortcut: <userinput><command>#fopen</command></userinput>, "
"which has the same effect as above."
msgstr ""
"एकः लघुमार्गः अपि अस्ति : <userinput><command>#fopen</command></userinput>, यस्य "
"प्रभावः उपरिष्टाद् समानः अस्ति ।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:74
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you do not find all your man pages, adjust the configuration file "
"<filename>/etc/manpath.config</filename> (or a file of a similar name "
"depending on your distribution) or adjust the environment variables "
"<envar>MANPATH</envar> and <envar>MANSECT</envar>."
msgstr ""
"यदि भवान् स्वस्य सर्वाणि man पृष्ठानि न प्राप्नोति तर्हि विन्याससञ्चिकां <filename>/etc/"
"manpath.config</filename> (अथवा भवतां वितरणस्य आधारेण समाननामस्य सञ्चिकां) "
"समायोजयन्तु अथवा वातावरणचरं <envar>MANPATH< समायोजयन्तु /envar> तथा "
"<envar>MANSECT</envar> इति ।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:82
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"As with any other KIO worker, it is possible to enter a &URL;, like "
"<userinput><command>man:/socket</command></userinput> in <emphasis>any</"
"emphasis> &kde; application. Try it in &kwrite; and you will see the man "
"page in &HTML; format."
msgstr ""
"अन्येषां KIO कार्यकर्तृणां इव &URL;प्रवेशः सम्भवति, यथा <userinput><command>man:/"
"socket</command></userinput> <emphasis>any</emphasis> &kde; अनुप्रयोगः। "
"&kwrite इत्यत्र प्रयतस्व; तथा च भवन्तः &HTML; प्रारूपम् ।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:89
#, no-c-format
msgid "Contact mailing list: <email>kde-devel@kde.org</email>"
msgstr "सम्पर्क मेलसूची : <email>kde-devel@kde.org</email>"
